profile:
Casa Suarez buys its unique furniture pieces wholesale in order to furnish the apartments managed by Corporate Stays. Because of this, Casa Suarez is able to offer these pieces for retail at a fraction of the normal cost to consumers.

Each piece from Casa Suarez is guaranteed to be of the highest quality, handmade from Indonesia and India. Corporate Stays relies on these pieces from Casa Suarez to welcome multiple travellers from across the world while maintaining their beauty and structural integrity.

Casa Suarez is so convinced of the quality of its furnishings that it offers a one-year guarantee on its furniture. Each piece of Casa Suarez furniture purchased new, is guaranteed for defects and structural integrity for one year following original purchase.
name: Casa Suarez
